Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL STORY BY NATSU HYUUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICION, AND ALL NAMES OF FIGURES ND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no understanding of chastity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a picky eater too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}-So cold! -The warming stones help a little, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To have nothing to do in this cold is torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is so chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least have some sort of tent…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This seating is made to foster hostility{\i} {\i1}among the four concubines.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. That lady is the Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite young, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she gave birth to the Lord at…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must've worked hard{\i} {\i1}to give birth to him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress Dowager has two children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord and his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's rumored that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the brother is very ill and can't leave the house often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he was here until recently, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You call this plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,An attendant is to serve her master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of dressing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the master who suffers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when her attendant looks poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those attendants are Lady Lihua's…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Yinghua's at it. They started a battle by proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Maomao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She even hired that ugly duckling, that's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ugly duckling? Is she talking about me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yinghua! -Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They haven't realized?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were so close at the Crystal Pavilion!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get too carried away,{\i} {\i1}I'll tell Father!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll make sure{\i} {\i1}you physically can't tell on anyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was just a courtesan joke…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you suddenly all quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? -You…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay, Maomao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know you're really this cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to switch warming stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only did she suffer misfortune,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she even mistrusts men so much{\i} {\i1}that she dirties her face…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She desperately suffered horrible bullying{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at the Crystal Pavilion for two months…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't complain once,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she doesn't want to worry us…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It makes sense that the kind-hearted{\i} {\i1}Sir Jinshi watches out for her!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're making up stories again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she even know her position?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that red clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another battle by proxy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Virtuous versus the Pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two groups don't get along well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Virtuous Concubine{\i} {\i1}is very young at 14,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while the Pure Concubine{\i} {\i1}is a veteran at 35.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course they don't get along!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And, they were formerly mother{\i} {\i1}and daughter-in-law.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and daughter-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So… This is a bit complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but the two Ladies were originally the former Emperor's concubine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the current Lord's concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the former Emperor passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Emperor's concubine became a monk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then came back as the current Emperor's concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Emperor passed away five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Concubine Ah-Duo, who was a Lady at the time, was 30-years-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Virtuous Concubine, Lishu, was nine at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's politics,{\i} {\i1}but to be married at nine…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it? A nine-year-old mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A nine-year-old mother-in-law…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who was concubine{\i} {\i1}to the former Emperor was…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Lishu?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that is the young mother-in-law?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Virtuous Concubine, Lady Lishu, is still quite young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Traditionally, the Virtuous Concubine{\i} {\i1}should be wearing white.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that dark pink color…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It clearly overlaps with Lady Gyokuyou, The Precious Concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she doesn't notice things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The warming stones were a big help. Please make them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're cold, you should have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking whether you can share with the attendants in the Crystal Pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You even asked for permission from Lady Gyokuyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A hair clip?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they recruit talented people hidden in the flower garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can have other meanings though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, it can have other meanings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess he's giving them out to everyone{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that no attendants are embarrassed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lihaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like a big dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a participation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not enough, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Goodbye, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Gyokuyou…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Might get a little more than upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be more higher-up than I imagined.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fits right in with all the soldiers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That soldier from before is there too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's in the last seat. He's young,{\i} {\i1}so he might have been promoted.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That glittery eunuch isn't here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that doesn't matter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, time for poison testing!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No cloudiness to the contact areas.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No strange scents, either.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But a poison tester's job isn't over{\i} {\i1}until she swallows…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now rinse my mouth with fresh water…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A poison tester's life is expendable.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who tastes poison{\i} {\i1}for fun.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If possible, I'd love some puffer fish!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sneaking its organs into soup….{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way it tingles my tongue{\i} {\i1}is irresistible!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Concentrate!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raw fish and vegetables.{\i} {\i1}The Emperor's favorite.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was served at the rear palace{\i} {\i1}sometimes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It usually contains blue fish,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but today it's jellyfish.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Food Service in charge of{\i} {\i1}the Emperor's meals{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would never mistake his favorite{\i} {\i1}ingredient.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Gyokuyou doesn't have any foods{\i} {\i1}she can't eat.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must've messed up{\i} {\i1}the food distribution.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't like fish?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess she can't leave anything uneaten{\i} {\i1}in front of the Emperor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I hadn't seen that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see, Lihaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That poison tester looks determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so fun about watching people eat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,while fearing for their lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That poison tester…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the girl from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How delicious is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Poison in the Precious Concubine's soup? -Is it really poisonous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison tester drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister! What are you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Formal wear is so uncomfortable…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Minister drank the soup and collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apothecary…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apothecary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Sir Jinshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no, I was excited by the poison.{\i} {\i1}It's like I smiled at him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To the medical room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I spit out the poison. There's nothing wrong with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I actually wanted to{\i} {\i1}swallow it right there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I had, the poison would be{\i} {\i1}circulating all around me…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Jinshi, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me the leftover soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ambitious, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After you left,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,someone doubted that it was poison, drank it, and collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What idiot did such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Minister. Now, people are panicking even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an antiemetic drug. You can vomit so much that your stomach turns around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a poison on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hair clip?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eunuchs get hair clips too?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,{\i} {\i1}his collar is disheveled.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not as glittery as usual.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this why I didn't see him{\i} {\i1}at the banquet?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now, he looks like{\i} {\i1}any young man his age…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, he looks quite young.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks better this way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It works! As expected of medicine{\i} {\i1}from the court doctor!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm all finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who put poison in Concubine Gyokuyou's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have someone I want you to bring about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you call Lady Lishu for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Jinshi. What did you need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for calling you to such an unrefined place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who we really wanted was that attendant there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it seafood you can't eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some who can't eat particular foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's soba noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you eat poison happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried hard to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my throat closes up,{\i} {\i1}and I can't breathe.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a little bit gives me a rash.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hard to adjust the amount,{\i} {\i1}and recovery is slow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what "not being able to eat" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Lishu. Is your stomach all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can offer you a laxative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The meal at the garden party was clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,prepared by the rear palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish and vegetable dish had different ingredients than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there was an error
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Lady Gyokuyou and Lady Lishu's meals got mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it mackerel you can't eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with being a picky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, hives were the only symptom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but it could cause difficulty breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew this and served it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as poisoning someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You. You're the poison tester, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered things to look out for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in case of emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the best bet is to not eat it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you mess up once,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even a physician can't resolve the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a life-or-death problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's enough blackmailing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm of low class. Please refrain from touching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who says such things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They just don't want you to feel hurt, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I must report to Lady Gyokuyou…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Why did you have the poison tester be present for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb. You said to call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so I could inform her of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that the servers simply made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not for a mere attendant to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At least tell me this, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The target was the Virtuous Concubine, Concubine Lishu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was no poison in any other plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this have something to do with the wood tablet incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no burns on that attendant just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW OF NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Next episode, "Homecoming."{\i}
